## Phase 2: VT 兼容性

### 当前代码状态盘点

**已有实现（term/mod.rs 1038 lines）：**
- CSI: A/B/C/D/E/F (cursor move), G/H/f/d (positioning), J/K (erase), S/T (scroll), L/M (insert/delete line), P/@/X (char edit), I/Z (tab), g (tab clear), r (DECSTBM), m (SGR), h/l (mode set/reset)
- ESC: 7/8 (save/restore cursor), c (RIS reset), D (IND), E (NEL), M (RI), H (HTS)
- OSC: 0/2 (title)
- DEC modes: 7 (auto wrap), 25 (cursor visible), 6 (origin), 1 (app cursor keys), 2004 (bracketed paste), 47/1047/1049 (alt screen — FLAG ONLY, no buffer swap!)

**关键缺口：**
1. alt_screen 只是 bool flag，没有真正的 alt Grid buffer swap
2. CSI 缺：DA (device attributes), DECSCUSR (cursor shape), REP (repeat char), SCP/RRCP (save/restore cursor position)
3. ESC 缺：DECALN (ESC # 8), G0/G1 charset designation (ESC ( B etc.)
4. Tab stops: CHA (CSI G) 已有，但 DECSTBM 后 scroll region 切换测试不足

### 任务详细设计

**P2-1 (dd_dev): Alt Screen Buffer**
```rust
// Terminal struct 改动：
pub struct Terminal {
    grid: Grid,
    alt_grid: Option<Grid>,        // NEW
    saved_cursor: Cursor,          // 已有，用于 ESC 7/8
    saved_cursor_alt: Cursor,      // NEW — for DECSET 1049 cursor save
    // ...
}

// set_dec_mode 改动：
47 | 1047 => {
    // swap grid pointer, don't save cursor
    if enable {
        if self.alt_grid.is_none() {
            self.alt_grid = Some(std::mem::take(&mut self.grid));
            self.grid = Grid::new(self.width(), self.height());
        }
    } else {
        if let Some(alt) = self.alt_grid.take() {
            self.grid = alt;
        }
    }
}
1049 => {
    if enable {
        // save cursor + switch to alt + clear
        self.saved_cursor_alt = self.cursor;
        // enter alt screen (same as 1047)
    } else {
        // switch back + restore cursor
        self.cursor = self.saved_cursor_alt;
    }
}
```
测试要求：
- t_alt_screen_swap: 写入主屏 → DECSET 1049 → 写入内容 → 验证主屏内容保留
- t_alt_screen_cursor_restore: DECSET 1049 → 移动 cursor → DECRST 1049 → 验证 cursor 恢复
- t_alt_screen_1...

